@startuml
!theme plain

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam noteBorderColor #CCCCCC
skinparam arrowColor #333333
skinparam sequence {
  LifeLineBorderColor #333333
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
  ParticipantBorderColor #333333
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantPadding 15
  BoxBorderColor #CCCCCC
  BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
}

title LingFlow 消息处理流程

participant "客户端" as Client
participant "服务端" as Server
participant "AWS" as AWS

== 1. 认证阶段 ==

Client -> Server: POST /api/auth/token\n{ "user_id": "xxx" }
Server -> Server: 验证用户身份
Server --> Client: { token, user_id }

== 2. WebSocket 连接 ==

Client -> Server: WS Connect ?token=xxx
Server -> Server: 验证 Token + Origin + IP限制
Server --> Client: 101 Switching Protocols

== 3. 技能列表推送 ==

Server -> AWS: LoadAllSkills()
AWS --> Server: 技能列表
Server --> Client: system_skills_list\n(技能列表推送)

== 4. 消息处理 ==

Client -> Server: user_chat\n{ message: "分析交易" }
Server -> Server: 技能匹配 (关键词检索)
Server --> Client: system_thinking\n{ phase: skill_selection }

Server -> AWS: Converse API\n(生成响应)
AWS --> Server: LLM 响应
Server --> Client: system_thinking\n{ phase: llm_generation }

Server --> Client: system_response\n{ content, tokens, latency }

== 5. 心跳检测 ==

Client -> Server: heartbeat_chat (ping)
Server --> Client: heartbeat_chat (pong)

@enduml